  <title>Tell Others About You With About.Me</title>
  <slug>tell-others-about-you-with-aboutme</slug>
  <author>abelgaxiola</author>
  <pubDate>2012-01-16 03:46:21</pubDate>
  <lastModified>2012-01-16 03:46:21</lastModified>
  <excerpt>Free website that allows you to share information about yourself.</excerpt>
  <content>&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;If you haven’t heard about the personal web hosting service named about.me don’t feel bad. I just recently found out about it while looking for a simple solution for hosting a personal blog. Wikipedia has it described as “a personal web hosting service that offers registered users a simple platform from which to link multiple online identities, relevant external sites, and popular social networking websites …”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;Two months ago I decided to give it a try and this is what I found:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote style="border: 0px; font-family: Georgia, &amp;quot;Bitstream Charter&amp;quot;, serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: italic; margin-right: 3em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 3em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: &amp;quot;&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&amp;quot;; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;· Easy to create a new account&lt;br /&gt;· Great single page to link multiple sites such as Twitter, Facebook, LinkedIn, and anything that has a web presence&lt;br /&gt;· Easy to create a nice looking one page site&lt;br /&gt;· Simple to update&lt;br /&gt;· Page loads fast – much faster than any of my blogging sites&lt;br /&gt;· It’s free&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;And if you hurry and create an account there is a good chance your name is still available. Yesterday I created three accounts just to test the availability of the available names and I was able to create the following:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote style="border: 0px; font-family: Georgia, &amp;quot;Bitstream Charter&amp;quot;, serif; font-size: 15px; font-style: italic; margin-right: 3em; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 3em; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: &amp;quot;&amp;quot; &amp;quot;&amp;quot;; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;For my wife: &lt;a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://about.me/noeliagaxiola" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;http://about.me/noeliagaxiola&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;For my last name: &lt;a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://about.me/gaxiola" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;http://about.me/gaxiola&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"&gt;For my sister: &lt;a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://about.me/xochitl" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;http://about.me/xochitl&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;I like the fact that by going to &lt;a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20130724015551/http://about.me/abelgaxiola" style="border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(25, 130, 209);"&gt;http://about.me/abelgaxiola&lt;/a&gt; I and anybody else has access to other online services that I decide to share. In my about.me page I’m sharing Twitter, Facebook, Google+, LinkedIn, and three of my websites.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="border: 0px; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 1.625em; outline: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(55, 55, 55);"&gt;My opinion: go ahead and create an account, spend 30 minutes making it look nice, create links to other personal web sites, and share with those that you think can benefit from this.&lt;/p&gt;</content>
